===Etymology 1===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*leyp-}}
From {{inh|en|enm|lyvere}}, {{m|enm|lyver}}, from {{inh|en|ang|lifer}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*librō}}, from {{der|gem-pro|ine-pro|*leyp-|t=to smear, smudge, stick}}, from {{der|gem-pro|ine-pro|*ley-|t=to be slimy, be sticky, glide}}. Cognate with {{cog|stq|Lieuwer|t=liver}}, {{cog|fy|lever|t=liver}}, {{cog|nl|lever|t=liver}}, {{cog|de|Leber|t=liver}}, {{cog|da|-}}, {{cog|no|-}} and {{cog|sv|lever|t=liver}} (the last three from {{cog|non|lifr|t=liver}}). Related to {{m|en|live}}.

